title: [Rambling Meadows, Orchard]
description: A sharp sweet odor pervades the neglected orchard, but the scent is not altogether unpleasant.  A half-buried wooden bucket lies partially hidden within a thick tuft of meadow grass at the base of a nearby tree.

A sharp sweet odor pervades the neglected orchard, but the scent is not altogether unpleasant.  Slender bone-like trunks sit coldly in the grassy earth, their twisted branches extended into the cool night air.  A half-buried wooden bucket lies partially hidden within a thick tuft of meadow grass at the base of a nearby tree.
